STM32CubeWL3
############

Origin:
   STMicroelectronics
   https://www.st.com/en/embedded-software/stm32cubewl3.html

Status:
   version v1.5.0

Purpose:
   STMicroelectronics official MCU package for STM32WL3x series.

Description:
   This package is an extract of official STM32CubeWL3 package written by STMicroelectronics.
   It is composed of STM32Cube hardware abstraction layer (HAL) and low layer (LL) drivers
   plus the CMSIS device headers for the STM32WL3x series: a top-level stm32wl3x.h and the
   device-group headers stm32wl3xx.h (STM32WL30/31/33) and stm32wl3rx.h (STM32WL3R).

Dependencies:
    None.

URL:
   https://github.com/STMicroelectronics/STM32CubeWL3

Commit:
   a9cdf2a35810b354c7c34d77465d862b9b8cd945

Maintained-by:
   External

